{"tid":800961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子患罹患眼癌致毀容 女友不離棄陪走最後人生路","createTime":"2018-08-31T09:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T17:50:17.000Z","uid":75969,"like":293,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b0f9d6c2f2de01e41ddc3688bacf0b57b4d873","tid":800961,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180831/_2018083114321414039.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180831%2F_2018083114321414039.jpg&d=shnVi3qh%2BggJmGL%2Bp7zlEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8524a349\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180831%2F_2018083114321414039.jpg&h=ada74178\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180831/_2018083114321414039.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n如果男友毀容，並非所有人都做到不離不棄。而泰國男子因罹患眼癌，臉部嚴重變形，令五官難以辨認。而女友三年半間一直陪伴在旁，直至男友前日日病逝，女友在Facebook發文表示「我真的很抱歉，我竟然沒有陪在你的身邊」。<br />\n<br />\n女子阿提塔雅（Atittaya Chumkeaw）男友21歲，三年前診斷出罹患視網膜母細胞瘤，該癌症傳播速度很快，導致雙眼凸出、臉腫大，視力及聽力都下降。該病屬於罕見，每年每百萬人僅五人感染。<br />\n<br />\n阿提塔雅剛得知男友得病時，每天都痛哭，不過後來決定坦然面對，並陪伴鼓舞男友，並不時在Facebook上發合照，包括今年2月時交往三周年的合照。不過病情越來越嚴重，男友身形也日漸消瘦，29日塔雅當時並不在泰國，而她接到男友家人的訊息，直到男友已經過世。塔雅在Facebook發文，並立即趕回泰國送男友最後一程。網民紛紛安慰，希望她能堅強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806161&d=shnVi3qh%2BggJmGL%2Bp7zlEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2e74f21c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806161&h=54173af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806161</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都肯陪到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933348214d1b5c743e88d1f4092b43786d77f3ff","tid":800961,"uid":124760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b270825a7074bf985ba61266a25431724ba673e","tid":800961,"uid":57410,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"哈利"},{"pid":"c4970859e9e7b7599ddd2f4c289211b93e2db997","tid":800961,"uid":121130,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"問世間情是何物"},{"pid":"424ba97488ae30895e54016bb68960e6e0aa0961","tid":800961,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":64,"score":-59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/180817_ac3fdc61bdab66098a1c77ef2ada5baf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F180817_ac3fdc61bdab66098a1c77ef2ada5baf.png&h=1167f2b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a57c5bf8a3454677e034e56849c25a3c89fbd596","tid":800961,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46e5fc1340ab6c55662fb7e11289515e13156a66","tid":800961,"uid":119330,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"天國的階梯"},{"pid":"644021dde24b3500478af49901aae507a28c67e7","tid":800961,"uid":191338,"like":11,"dislike":215,"score":-204,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/181707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F181707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8ca376c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d63e3371f4978618c920fcbb68c85985dde09f4b","tid":800961,"uid":14423,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:18:4