:"2018-09-01T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"明明巴魯坦星人係一個萌角"},{"pid":"7e52eeced9a7fe89dd8367a4273657a1445217f1","tid":800961,"uid":91693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c6d0f507cbb2d8bc85e15254fe423d582f082ef","tid":800961,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"644021dde24b3500478af49901aae507a28c67e7","tid":800961,"uid":191338,"like":11,"dislike":215,"score":-204,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/181707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F181707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8ca376c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9312fd526d01146f16f10b749b000917b460d4","tid":800961,"uid":121126,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180831/_2018083114321414039.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180831%2F_2018083114321414039.jpg&d=shnVi3qh%2BggJmGL%2Bp7zlEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8524a349\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180831%2F_2018083114321414039.jpg&h=ada74178\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180831/_2018083114321414039.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n如果男友毀容，並非所有人都做到不離不棄。而泰國男子因罹患眼癌，臉部嚴重變形，令五官難以辨認。而女友三年半間一直陪伴在旁，直至男友前日日病逝，女友在Facebook發文表示「我真的很抱歉，我竟然沒有陪在你的身邊」。<br />\n<br />\n女子阿提塔雅（Atittaya Chumkeaw）男友21歲，三年前診斷出罹患視網膜母細胞瘤，該癌症傳播速度很快，導致雙眼凸出、臉腫大，視力及聽力都下降。該病屬於罕見，<span style=\"color: red;\">每年每百萬人僅五人感染</span>。<br />\n<br />\n阿提塔雅剛得知男友得病時，每天都痛哭，不過後來決定坦然面對，並陪伴鼓舞男友，並不時在Facebook上發合照，包括今年2月時交往三周年的合照。不過病情越來越嚴重，男友身形也日漸消瘦，29日塔雅當時並不在泰國，而她接到男友家人的訊息，直到男友已經過世。塔雅在Facebook發文，並立即趕回泰國送男友最後一程。網民紛紛安慰，希望她能堅強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806161&d=shnVi3qh%2BggJmGL%2Bp7zlEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2e74f21c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806161&h=54173af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806161</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都肯陪到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n癌症係感染返黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c4350c3b38aa62e25fa92affd70f6508650aeb","tid":800961,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"咁靚仔都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip"},{"pid":"2c1adc5f8078c138604906881f3855333a9f489c","tid":800961,"uid":18955,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"係香港呢啲地方<br />\n一早就反面唔認人<br />\n去搵定下家埋單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先不論外貌身材<br />\n呢個重情重義嘅女仔<br />\n一定係上帝嘅禮物"},{"pid":"1ac6d4f439c37ef252c9449fc20e9b9dc680de82","tid":800961,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"仲要陪佢3年 難得"},{"pid":"61b91ecd4ea30d4f5a38d57dbe22cff6f0d98248","tid":800961,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:2